<span rend="jisage_7" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 7em"><span rend="naka-midashi" rendition="h"><span rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi20">二</span></span></span>
<lb />
　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">弟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おとうと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は、どうせ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぬなら、いっそ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鬼</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にでも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">食</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">く</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>われて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">死</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">し</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>んでしまったほうがいいと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>いました。それにしても、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">何</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>十<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">里</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">り</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>あるかわかりませんでした。<lb />
